title: One of the best community
description: I think EddieHub is one of the first community which introduces me to a whole new world of open source and made me realize that we all can work in a collaborative and exclusive environment no matter how professional or novice we are. This is a place for all, No matter who you are beginner or a professional you should definitely checkout EddieHub community and do contribute to it, start it or sponsor it. It will make you fall in love with open source specially Eddie - he is the best my bet.
